 <fr:p>Fixing <fr:tex>x:B</fr:tex>, we must show that <fr:tex>\mathchoice { \textstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( y:B \right ) \mathclose {} } }{ \textstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( y:B \right ) \mathclose {} } }{ \scriptstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( y:B \right ) \mathclose {} } }{ \scriptscriptstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( y:B \right ) \mathclose {} } } gx \approx _{ \mathcal {A} } gy</fr:tex> is a <fr:link
href="erct-001I.xml"
type="local"
addr="erct-001I">proposition</fr:link>. But this is a <fr:link
href="erct-001I.xml"
type="local"
addr="erct-001I">retract</fr:link> of  <fr:tex>\mathchoice { \textstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( y:A \right ) \mathclose {} } }{ \textstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( y:A \right ) \mathclose {} } }{ \scriptstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( y:A \right ) \mathclose {} } }{ \scriptscriptstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( y:A \right ) \mathclose {} } } gx \approx _{ \mathcal {A} } y</fr:tex>, which is a <fr:link
